org.afplib.afplib

Interface MetricAdjustment

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Triplet
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MetricAdjustmentImpl

    public interface MetricAdjustment
extends Triplet
    A representation of the model object 'Metric Adjustment'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Unit Base
    • XUPUB
    • YUPUB
    • HUniform Increment
    • VUniform Increment
    • HBaseline Increment
    • VBaseline Increment

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getMetricAdjustment()
